<item>
            <title>[LU-6862] Improve dist tarball inclusion of contrib subdirectory</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6862</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It looks like authors and reviewers of patches adding things to the contrib subdirectory have been inconsistent with the inclusion of the contrib tree&apos;s contents in the distribution tarball.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To help keep things consistent, I will remove the Makefiles from the contrib tree and instead just list contrib under EXTRA_DIST at the top level.  That will simply include everything added to contrib in the dist tarball.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
